Host *
     ForwardAgent no
     ForwardX11 no
     ForwardX11Trusted yes
     User nixcraft
     Port 22
     Protocol 2
     ServerAliveInterval 60
     ServerAliveCountMax 30


Host github.com
    HostName github.com
    PreferredAuthentications publickey
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/github

# Work GitHub
Host work.github.com
    HostName github.com
    PreferredAuthentications publickey
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa_work
